These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
7 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, goldfish, hamster, horse, pony, rabbit
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, golf, parkour, surfing, tennis, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the lizard##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the owner of the pony is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the owner of the horse##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Pet   | lizard  | hamster        | turtle  | rabbit     | pony   | goldfish       | horse   |
| Sport         | golf   | water-polo | surfing    | parkour  | tennis | volleyball | climbing |

