.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
City: liverpool, san-francisco, edinburgh, hamburg, hannover, paris, berlin
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, animation, drama, musical, scientific, zombie
There are 7 different nationalities: american, egyptian, french, indian, italian, mexican, turkish
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the french is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the mexican is the person watching action movies##1
10. the american is the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the turkish##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| City          | san-francisco  | paris    | hannover  | liverpool | hamburg  | berlin | edinburgh |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation | zombie   | drama   | scientific | action     | adventure |
| Nationality   | italian | turkish   | american | french  | egyptian   | mexican    | indian    |

