 4. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the pony##2
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the train##1
