 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
