There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, emerald, green, pink, lavender, brown, blood-red
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes green##2
 3. the person who likes turquise is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the writer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
14. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Color   | blood-red | green        | brown    | lavender     | pink     | emerald   | turquise        |
| Pet           | bird   | ferret       | mouse    | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake   | chinchilla |

