11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the british is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the american and the person who's hobby is writing##2
